snippet.textDisplay: This was way, way better than it has any right to be. Three more or less novice presenters, handful of crew, and virtually no budget.. yet the production values, the presenting, the editing, the content, is as good as, if not better than hugely bank rolled TV shows with seasoned presenters and a credits list into the hundreds. Amazing job, love it.
